Relationship management commands for episodes

Usage: do-memory-cli relationship <COMMAND>

Commands:
  add       Add a relationship between two episodes
  remove    Remove a relationship by its ID
  list      List relationships for an episode
  find      Find episodes related to a given episode
  info      Get detailed information about a relationship
  graph     Generate a dependency graph for an episode
  validate  Validate relationships for cycles
  help      Print this message or the help of the given subcommand(s)

Options:
  -h, --help  Print help
